Green Prosperity 2 is a server developed by Eclipse and Tacos to the players desire. We don't only add things that we believe will make things fun, we also add things to the players desire. Which means that if a player wants something, all they have to do is post it on the forums and we'll try our best to add it.

Game Tickets with Game Chest Elite Game Tickets with Elite Game Chest
Zombie Minigame Zombie King (New Boss) Zombie Points Shop
